org.opentrafficsim.graphs

Class ContinuousColorPaintScale

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opentrafficsim.graphs.ContinuousColorPaintScale
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.jfree.chart.renderer.PaintScale

    public class ContinuousColorPaintScale
extends Object
implements org.jfree.chart.renderer.PaintScale
    Create a continuous color paint scale.
    Primarily intended for the contour plots, but sufficiently abstract for more general use.
    A continuous color paint scale creates paints (actually simple Colors) by linearly interpolating between a limited set of RGB Color values that correspond to given input values.
